Revision history for Dancer-Template-Haml

0.02    [enosis]
        Wed Oct 27 16:00:00 PST 2010
        - Facility for defining and activating Haml filters and helpers

0.01_02 [enosis]
        Wed Oct 27 15:30:00 PST 2010
        - Dancer::Template::Abstract defines the interface to render()
          as: (a) a reference to string, or (b) a string path to file.

0.01_01 [enosis]
        Wed Jul 21 14:00:00 PST 2010
        - Adjust for change moving methods view() and template() 
          from Dancer::Helpers to Dancer::Template::Abstract.
          <http://github.com/sukria/Dancer/commit/ddbdc768c15e6196c05465689f30c0ffc42b32ba>
          This revision supports appending a missing .haml suffix.
          render() no longer converts s/.tt$/.haml/ 

0.01    Mon Feb  8 14:40:15 EST 2010
        - original version

